<br>
The stuff we fight, there's usually a good risk of a wipe, so we always have two others keep their MGB up in case of a wipe.<br>
<br>
That's 4 clerics so far.<br>
<br>
Any other clerics on our raids, sure I guess they could cast EE using MGB, but... in our situation, with the difficulty level of mobs we normally fight, and the average hps of everyone on the raid, having an AE heal for 1200 every 72 minutes just wouldn't be worth it. =)<br>
<br>
Not saying it's not helpful in some situations, especially for guilds still doing stuff like HoT in ToV. The only problem there is, how many &quot;younger&quot; guilds have more than 4 L60 clerics with MGB?<br>
<br>
IMO, situationally it could be of use, but I wouldn't classify it as a normal usage. =)<br>
<br>
